    full_citation: 'Koole SN, van Stein RM, Sikorska K, et al. Primary cytoreductive surgery with or without hyperthermic intraperitoneal chemotherapy for stage III ovarian cancer (OVHIPEC-2). N Engl J Med. 2023;389(6):473–482.',
