    key_result: 'BAP1-mutated mesothelioma: median OS not reached at 5 years vs BAP1-wild type: median OS 28 months (p=0.003). BAP1 loss: paradoxically associated with improved prognosis in peritoneal mesothelioma (opposite of pleural). Germline BAP1 mutations in 13% of cohort.',
