    background: 'Peritoneal mesothelioma outcomes vary widely even within epithelioid histology, and no robust molecular prognostic marker existed. BAP1 alterations were known to influence mesothelioma biology, but their prognostic direction in the peritoneal (versus pleural) compartment was unclear, as was the frequency of hereditary predisposition.',
