    practice_impact: 'Will determine whether HIPEC benefit demonstrated at IDS in OVHIPEC-1 extends to the primary surgery setting. If positive, would support universal HIPEC at all cytoreductive surgery time points for ovarian cancer. Currently OVHIPEC-1 (IDS setting) remains the primary evidence base.',
