    key_result: 'CRS+HIPEC recommended for epithelioid MPeM with PCI <20 and adequate PS. Cisplatin-based HIPEC (200–250 mg/m² ± doxorubicin) at 41–43°C for 60–90 min endorsed. Sarcomatoid histology: contraindication. BAP1 testing mandatory. Immunotherapy (nivolumab+ipilimumab) recommended for systemic therapy. Pemetrexed+cisplatin as first-line systemic option.',
